65ccfe4f94aa8ee8e84b591d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20thing%20about%20a%20lifetime%20of%20shame%20is%20that%20you%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20heavy%20a%20burden%20it%20is%20until%20the%20moment%20you%20set%20it%20down.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Vades%20Joseph%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sidewalk%20was%20empty%2C%20so%20no%20one%20could%20see%20me%20crying%20outside%20Levain%20Bakery's%20soaring%20glass%20doors.%20But%20there%20was%20nothing%20to%20shield%20me%20from%20the%20staff%20inside%20watching%20me%2C%20stunned%2C%20sobbing%2C%20giddy%20with%20excitement%20about%20what%20a%20drug%20had%20done%20to%20my%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20count%20how%20many%20times%20Levain's%20cookies%20sabotaged%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20day%20of%20disciplined%20dieting%20broken%20as%20I%20got%20sucked%20into%20those%20buttery%20black%20holes.%20Often%20I%20fought%20the%20temptation%3B%20sometimes%20I%20won%2C%20but%20too%20frequently%20I%20felt%20my%20body%20pulse%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-dopamine-restricting-for-procrastination-motivation-productivity-strategy-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edopamine%3C%2Fa%3E%20reward%20(mouth%20salivating%2C%20throat%20tensing)%20before%20caving%20to%20the%20cookies%2C%20resenting%20my%20choice%2C%20and%20feeling%20the%20familiar%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20suddenly%20didn't%20care%20about%20stepping%20inside%2C%20I%20didn't%20trust%20it.%20I%20forced%20myself%20to%20visualize%20that%20first%20perfect%20bite%2C%20waiting%20for%20my%20mouth%20to%20water%20and%20jaw%20to%20ache%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20nothing.%20When%20it%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20I%20could%20win%20my%20daily%20battle%20without%20even%20fighting%20it%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20learned%20how%20to%20breathe%20underwater%2C%20as%20if%20I'd%20lost%20enough%20weight%20to%20levitate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20skeptical%20about%20last%20year's%20glowing%20articles%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOzempic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20GLP-1%20medications.%20Like%20so%20many%20chronically%20overweight%20people%2C%20I'd%20seen%20it%20all%20and%20then%20some%3A%20stimulants%2C%20supplements%2C%20low-carb%2C%20low-fat%2C%20intermittent%20fasting%2C%20even%20laxatives.%20But%20these%20medications%20are%20nothing%20like%20what%20I%20expected.%20They're%20not%20really%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20at%20all.%20They're%20something%20far%20more%20powerful%20and%20surreal%3A%20injectable%20willpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGLP-1s'%20increasing%20popularity%20won't%20just%20mean%20that%20millions%20of%20us%20who've%20beat%20ourselves%20up%20for%20being%20overweight%20will%20be%20able%20to%20win%20that%20lifelong%20battle.%20It%20will%20mean%20fundamentally%20reevaluating%20our%20conception%20of%20free%20will%20and%20human%20agency%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reckoning%20with%20our%20tortured%20relationship%20with%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20diet%20culture%2C%20of%20our%20culture%20writ%20large%2C%20belittles%20the%20choices%20we%20make%20about%20food.%20What%20happens%2C%20then%2C%20when%20a%20drug%20reveals%20that%20eating%2C%20gambling%2C%20and%20so%20many%20other%20behaviors%20aren't%20choices%20at%20all%3F%20Just%20like%20when%20Prozac%20dismantled%20the%20myth%20that%20depression%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20or%20when%20earlier%20scientific%20advancements%20disproved%20the%20idea%20that%20illnesses%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.simonandschuster.com%2Fbooks%2FThe-Emperor-of-All-Maladies%2FSiddhartha-Mukherjee%2F9781439170915%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecancer%20were%20moral%20indictments%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20GLP-1s%20and%20similar%20medications%20are%20changing%20our%20shared%20sense%20of%20what%20is%20blameworthy%20and%20what%20is%20biology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20never%20have%20struggled%20%E2%80%94%20seriously%20struggled%20%E2%80%94%20with%20weight%2C%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20just%20how%20futile%20most%20weight-loss%20strategies%20are.%20Though%20people%20can%20%26quot%3Bsucceed%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20diet%20for%20months%2C%20maybe%20even%20a%20year%2C%20many%20dieters%20eventually%20regain%20weight.%20Most%20of%20the%20dozens%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-diet-food-list-cheap-easy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20diets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20health%20schemes%20I've%20been%20on%20over%20more%20than%2030%20years%20have%20helped%20for%20a%20time%2C%20but%20they%20all%20set%20me%20up%20to%20fail.%20For%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20only%20evidence-based%20strategy%20for%20safe%2C%20long-term%20weight%20management%20was%20surgery.%20But%20gastric%20surgery%20is%20expensive%20and%20painful%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3470459%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emany%20patients%20end%20up%20regaining%20weight%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20weight%20often%20has%20no%20bearing%20on%20health.%20For%20decades%20the%20fat-acceptance%20and%20fat-rights%20movements%20highlighted%20how%20size%20discrimination%20affects%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20around%20the%20world.%20Anti-fat%20bias%20costs%20people%20jobs%2C%20relationships%2C%20access%20to%20public%20spaces%2C%20and%20more.%20Fat-shaming%20and%20size%20discrimination%20also%20fuel%20eating%20disorders%20that%20affect%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanad.org%2Feating-disorder-statistic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ekill%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20Americans%20annually%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20even%20as%20diet%20culture%20is%20deadly%20for%20some%20and%20discriminatory%20for%20countless%20more%2C%20many%20of%20us%20have%20a%20medical%20need%20to%20lose%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20everything%20changed%20during%20my%20physical%20%E2%80%94%20shocking%20cholesterol%20numbers%20turned%20into%20specialist%20visits%2C%20then%20a%20grim%20warning%20that%20I%20was%20cutting%20my%20life%20short.%20So%20I%20started%20on%20a%20massive%20project%20of%20weight%20loss%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20lifestyle%20change.%20I%20set%20up%20a%20tracking%20sheet%20with%20a%20friend%3B%20we%20concocted%20a%20set%20of%20prizes%20for%20weeks%20when%20we%20were%20healthy%20and%20punishments%20for%20when%20we%20did%20badly.%20Having%20read%20so%20many%20studies%20about%20the%20failure%20rate%20for%20dieting%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20needed%20something%20that%20would%20truly%20terrify%20me%20if%20I%20seriously%20slipped.%20So%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemoth.org%2Fstories%2Fwith-a-little-help-from-my-nemesis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20out%20a%20check%20for%20%2410%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20organization%20I%20hated%20most%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20National%20Rifle%20Association%2C%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20my%20friend.%20Through%20the%20combination%20of%20incentives%2C%20accountability%2C%20social%20pressure%2C%20and%20the%20mental%20image%20of%20Wayne%20LaPierre%20gleefully%20cashing%20my%20check%2C%20I%20lost%2070%20pounds%20and%20even%20ran%20a%20marathon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20couldn't%20outrun%20the%20statistics%2C%20and%20during%20COVID-19%20isolation%20I%20lost%20so%20much%20of%20the%20progress%20I'd%20made.%20(No%2C%20the%20NRA%20never%20got%20a%20penny.)%20Even%20after%20the%20lockdown%20era%2C%20as%20I%20went%20running%20and%20lifted%20weights%20every%20week%2C%20I%20couldn't%20really%20make%20a%20dent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Albert%20Fox%20Cahn%20in%20front%20of%20Levain%20Bakery.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ccff056fcb546d2d4fc6a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20it%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20I%20could%20win%20my%20daily%20battle%20with%20temptation%20without%20even%20fighting%20it%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20learned%20how%20to%20breathe%20underwater%2C%20as%20if%20I'd%20lost%20enough%20weight%20to%20levitate.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Vades%20Joseph%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend's%20experience%20after%20our%20health%20challenge%20was%20very%20different.%20In%20early%202022%2C%20he%20began%20taking%20Ozempic.%20The%20injectable%20drug%20simulates%20GLP-1%2C%20a%20hormone%20regulating%20metabolism.%20Soon%20after%2C%20my%20friend%20switched%20to%20Mounjaro%2C%20which%20also%20simulates%20a%20second%20hormone%20called%20gastric%20inhibitory%20polypeptide%2C%20or%20GIP.%20The%20results%20were%20staggering.%20While%20I%20went%20from%20one%20gimmicky%20diet%20to%20the%20next%2C%20giving%20up%20carbs%20and%20then%20intermittently%20fasting%2C%20my%20friend%20was%20losing%20weight%20week%20over%20week%20with%20seemingly%20no%20rules%20or%20restrictions.%20By%20last%20summer%20I%20felt%20so%20stuck%2C%20enervated%2C%20and%20even%20desperate%20that%20I%20gave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fmounjaro%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520doctor%2520lost%252050%2520pounds%2Cfor%2520taking%2520blood%252Dpressure%2520medicine.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMounjaro%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiraculously%2C%20in%20less%20than%20a%20week%20I%20got%20a%20script%20from%20my%20doctor.%20My%20insurance%20would%20help%20cover%20the%20cost%3B%20I%20didn't%20need%20preauthorization.%20The%20clerk%20at%20my%20CVS%20said%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20they'd%20see%20someone%20spend%20just%20%2420%20for%20a%20drug%20that%20usually%20retails%20for%20%241%2C000%20to%20%241%2C200%20a%20month.%20I%20was%20extremely%20lucky.%20Many%20health%20plans%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fwegovy-ozempic-mounjaro-shortage-insurance-64014bc2887a518b33c597b2bf936e37%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erefused%20to%20cover%20GLP-1s%20for%20weight%20loss%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20limited%20approval%20from%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration.%20But%20prescribing%20GLP-1s%20%26quot%3Boff%20label%26quot%3B%20for%20weight%20loss%20is%20legal%2C%20and%20the%20surge%20in%20popularity%20has%20led%20to%20%3Cu%3Edrug%20shortages%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Sadly%2C%20many%20of%20those%20most%20at%20risk%20from%20obesity-related%20illness%20and%20diabetes%20have%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20accessing%20the%20medication.%20And%20as%20with%20every%20other%20aspect%20of%20American%20medicine%2C%20the%20impact%20is%20most%20acute%20for%20those%20from%20low-income%20communities%20of%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20squeamish%20holding%20the%20glow-stick-sized%20autoinjector%2C%20still%20cold%20from%20the%20fridge.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20pointing%20a%20loaded%20gun%20at%20the%20oversized%20belly%20I%20despised.%20I%20took%20a%20breath%2C%20pressed%20a%20button%2C%20braced%20for%20the%20pain%2C%20and%20%E2%80%A6%20felt%20almost%20nothing.%20It%20was%20so%20underwhelming%20that%20I%20called%20my%20friend%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20hadn't%20screwed%20it%20up.%20Then%20I%20went%20about%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20began%20the%20next%20morning.%20In%20the%20frantic%20deluge%20of%20emails%20and%20Zooms%2C%20I%20forgot%20about%20breakfast.%20By%202%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20I%20realized%20I'd%20been%20going%20since%206%20a.m.%20without%20a%20bite%20and%20still%20wasn't%20hungry.%20When%20I%20went%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20I%20was%20even%20more%20startled%20to%20see%20the%20coffee%20pot%20almost%20untouched.%20As%20a%20young%20lawyer%20I'd%20learned%20to%20exist%20off%20coffee%2C%20going%20through%20two%2C%20sometimes%20three%20pots%20of%20stovetop%20espresso%20a%20day.%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20my%20coffee%20habit%20as%20an%20addiction%20or%20poor%20impulse%20control%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20what%20my%20body%20wanted%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20pace%20of%20work.%20But%20suddenly%20my%20choices%20were%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20my%20building%20to%20grab%20lunch%2C%20passed%20Levain%2C%20and%20still%20felt%20nothing%2C%20the%20enormity%20of%20my%20changed%20decisions%20hit%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20about%20a%20lifetime%20of%20shame%20is%20that%20you%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20heavy%20a%20burden%20it%20is%20until%20the%20moment%20you%20set%20it%20down.%20If%20you'd%20asked%20me%20what%20I%20thought%20about%20weight%20pre-Mounjaro%2C%20I%20would've%20said%20it%20was%20frustrating%20but%20generally%20no%20big%20deal.%20Sure%2C%20I%20struggled%20with%20diet%20and%20impulses%2C%20but%20didn't%20everyone%3F%20Only%20a%20day%20after%20the%20first%20injection%2C%20I%20realized%20just%20how%20much%20pain%20I'd%20carried%20with%20my%20pounds%2C%20and%20how%20the%20humiliation%20of%20obesity%20had%20become%20central%20to%20how%20I%20defined%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20when%20I%20first%20became%20overweight%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20the%20moment%20I%20was%20taught%20to%20be%20ashamed%20of%20it.%20It%20was%20Halloween%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20us%208-year-olds%20went%20through%20the%20uniquely%20New%20York%20take%20on%20the%20holiday%20by%20pillaging%20dozens%20of%20walk-up%20apartments.%20We%20started%20on%20the%20top%20floor%20of%20the%20converted%20customs%20warehouse%20I%20called%20home%20in%20Greenwich%20Village%20before%20darting%20across%20town%20to%20the%20motherlode%3A%20my%20friend's%2020-story%2C%20500-unit%20building.%20Hours%20later%20we%20had%20bags%20of%20candy%20almost%20as%20large%20as%20we%20were.%20I%20sat%20down%20on%20my%20friend's%20couch%20to%20savor%20the%20first%20piece%20of%20the%20night%20%E2%80%94%20only%2C%20as%20I%20tore%20the%20red%20wrapper%20off%20the%20Kit%20Kat%2C%20a%20familiar%20voice%20behind%20me%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo.%26quot%3B%20I%20stammered%20some%20confused%20question%3A%20Why%20couldn't%20I%20start%20when%20everyone%20else%20was%20stuffing%20their%20face%3F%20%26quot%3BBecause%20you're%20fat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20voice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20they're%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shame%20of%20that%20moment%20stuck%20with%20me%20for%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20a%20funhouse%20mirror%20that%20transformed%20me%20from%20a%20child%20into%20a%20pig.%20It%20became%20an%20unshakable%20part%20of%20what%20I%20conceived%20as%20my%20essential%20self.%20I%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfat%20kid.%26quot%3B%20Once%20I%20internalized%20that%20label%2C%20it%20became%20indelible.%20No%20matter%20what%20my%20actual%20weight%20was%2C%20I%20viewed%20it%20through%20that%20lens%20of%20moral%20failure.%20Being%20overweight%2C%20obese%2C%20and%20eventually%20morbidly%20obese%20felt%20like%20destiny%2C%20the%20inevitable%20byproduct%20of%20my%20failure%20to%20prioritize%20my%20health%20over%20my%20appetite.%20Even%20when%20I%20dieted%2C%20went%20on%20health%20kicks%2C%20or%20even%20ran%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Marathon%2C%20I%20still%20thought%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20profoundly%20flawed%20person%2C%20because%20of%20the%20food%20choices%20I%20wanted%20to%20make.%20The%20fat-shaming%20I%20encountered%20as%20a%20child%20was%20a%20part%20of%20me%20no%20matter%20how%20far%20I%20ran%20or%20how%20hard%20I%20dieted.%20And%20with%20that%20first%20Mounjaro%20injection%2C%20it%20began%20to%20disappear.%20I%20saw%20that%20while%20grown-ups%20and%20doctors%20had%20blamed%20me%20for%20overeating%2C%20my%20own%20biology%20had%20set%20me%20up%20to%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20define%20yourself%20by%20being%20overweight%2C%20by%20your%20sense%20of%20weakness%20and%20failure%2C%20it%20warps%20how%20you%20view%20every%20other%20aspect%20of%20life.%20By%20nearly%20any%20measure%2C%20I'm%20a%20very%20driven%20person.%20After%20graduating%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-mba-program-grads-getting-jobs-drops-stanford-chicago-careers-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%3C%2Fa%3E%20Law%20School%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20one%20of%20the%20top%20law%20firms%20in%20the%20country%20before%20founding%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stopspying.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecivil-rights%20nonprofit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20run%20dozens%20of%20long-distance%20races%2C%20appeared%20in%20hundreds%20of%20TV%20segments%2C%20vied%20at%20a%20dozen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemoth.org%2Fstorytellers%2Falbert-fox-kahn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMoth%20story%20slams%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20I%20still%20thought%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20lazy%2C%20undisciplined%20person.%20Sure%2C%20I%20ran%2030%20miles%20a%20week%2C%20but%20it%20was%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bfat-guy%20pace.%26quot%3B%20Sure%2C%20I%20played%20tennis%20for%20four%2C%20five%2C%20even%20six%20hours%20a%20weekend%2C%20but%20I%20was%20doing%20the%20%26quot%3Beasy%26quot%3B%20clinic.%20At%20work%2C%20body%20image%20fueled%20the%20imposter%20syndrome%20that%20discounted%20what%20I%20built.%20And%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20where%20to%20begin%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20cacophony%20of%20chaos%20I%20call%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20those%20feelings%20didn't%20disappear%20the%20instant%20I%20injected%20the%20first%20shot%2C%20but%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%20I%20could%20see%20them%20at%20arm's%20length%2C%20mapping%20the%20tenuous%20threads%20that%20tethered%20them%20to%20painful%20childhood%20memories.%20No%20matter%20how%20many%20times%20you're%20told%20that%20everyone's%20metabolism%20is%20different%2C%20you%20don't%20truly%20believe%20it%20until%20the%20moment%20you%20feel%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F01%2F31%2Fopinion%2Fozempic-weight-loss-drugs.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enoted%20the%20questions%20these%20drugs%20raise%20about%20free%20will%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20but%20many%20of%20these%20conversations%20have%20missed%20the%20role%20that%20shame%20plays%20in%20how%20we%20see%20weight.%20These%20drugs%20can%20reprogram%20not%20only%20how%20our%20brains%20make%20choices%20but%20how%20we%20view%20ourselves.%20They%20can%20stop%20the%20vicious%20feedback%20loop%20where%20our%20food%20choices%20and%20weight%20drive%20the%20shame%20that%20drives%20our%20food%20choices%20and%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20seeing%20my%20own%20response%20to%20Mounjaro%2C%20I%20wasn't%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20researchers%20are%20investigating%20whether%20GLP-1s%20can%20treat%20addictions%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbpspubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fbph.15677%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edrugs%2C%20alcohol%2C%20smoking%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fcould-new-weight-loss-drugs-like-ozempic-treat-addiction1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egambling%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20people%20have%20even%20reported%20that%20they've%20helped%20control%20compulsive%20behaviors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fcould-new-weight-loss-drugs-like-ozempic-treat-addiction1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eskin%20picking%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20data%20is%20preliminary%2C%20and%20these%20drugs%20might%20not%20work%20for%20all%20these%20conditions.%20Still%2C%20it%20seems%20clear%20that%20these%20medications%20can%20help%20shape%20our%20behaviors%20in%20a%20way%20that%20wasn't%20possible.%20That's%20where%20the%20truly%20tough%20questions%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGLP-1s%20highlights%20how%20often%20we%20blame%2C%20even%20punish%2C%20people%20for%20choices%20that%20aren't%20truly%20their%20own.%20And%20this%20goes%20far%20beyond%20food.%20Most%20legal%20scholars%20think%20that%20punishment%20is%20unjust%20without%20blameworthiness%2C%20but%20so%20many%20of%20those%20in%20our%20prisons%20and%20jails%20are%20arrested%20because%20of%20an%20addiction.%20We%20pretend%20we%20can%20delineate%20the%20brain%20and%20the%20body%2C%20untangling%20what's%20choice%20and%20what's%20craving.%20But%20it's%20a%20farce.%20Those%20with%20serious%20addictions%20(and%20their%20families)%20have%20long%20understood%20that%20biology%20and%20cognition%20are%20linked.%20GLP-1s%20will%20give%20millions%20more%20this%20crucial%20insight%2C%20bringing%20so%20much%20of%20our%20criminal%20system%20into%20question.%20Blameworthiness%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshow%2Fhow-crime-works%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminalization%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20why%20(at%20least%20in%20theory)%20we%20don't%20punish%20people%20for%20crimes%20they%20commit%20by%20accident%2C%20when%20incapacitated%2C%20or%20held%20at%20gunpoint.%20Viewed%20through%20the%20GLP-1%20lens%2C%20so%20much%20of%20our%20legal%20system%20looks%20like%20Stephen%20Spielberg's%20%26quot%3BMinority%20Report.%26quot%3B%20The%20film%20posited%20a%20bleak%20future%20where%20suspects%20were%20arrested%20for%20pre-crimes%20they%20had%20not%20yet%20committed%2C%20but%20would%20commit%20one%20day.%20Watching%20the%20movie%2C%20it%20feels%20so%20wrong%20to%20imprison%20people%20who%20haven't%20even%20chosen%20to%20break%20the%20law.%20And%20that%20same%20feeling%20could%20impact%20how%20we%20view%20the%20prosecution%20of%20DUIs%2C%20drug%20offenses%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Albert%20Fox%20Cahn.%