0the%20status%20quo.%20While%20many%20people%20who%20stop%20using%20GLP-1s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.lww.com%2Febp%2Fcitation%2F2023%2F05000%2Fis_there_sustained_weight_loss_after.7.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estart%20to%20put%20back%20on%20the%20pounds%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20managed%20not%20to%20regain%20weight.%20It%20was%20a%20hollow%20victory%2C%20though%2C%20because%20it%20was%20a%20month%20of%20agony.%20I%20constantly%20forced%20myself%20to%20turn%20away%20from%20the%20things%20I%20wanted%2C%20to%20ignore%20the%20endless%20array%20of%20temptations.%20But%20no%20matter%20how%20heavy%20that%20burden%20was%2C%20one%20thing%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20bear%3A%20I%20wasn't%20weighed%20down%20by%20my%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Falbert-fox-cahn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAlbert%20Fox%20Cahn%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Surveillance%20Technology%20Oversight%20Project%2C%20or%20STOP%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20civil-rights%20and%20privacy%20group.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-ozempic-mounjaro-taught-me-about-my-brain-shame-willpower-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707994861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ccfe4f94aa8ee8e84b591d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-ozempic-mounjaro-taught-me-about-my-brain-shame-willpower-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20knew%20weight-loss%20drugs%20would%20change%20my%20body.%20I%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20what%20they%20would%20do%20to%20my%20brain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Albert%20Fox%20Cahn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A