u%20don't%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20connection%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20like%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20about%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20matter%20when%20I%20was%2025%2C%20because%20I%20wasn't%20planning%20on%20working%20that%20long.%20Who%20cares%20if%20it%20doesn't%20help%20my%20career%3F%20Because%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20have%20much%20of%20a%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20I%20have%20found%20a%20career%20and%20an%20employer%20that%20are%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20me%2C%20I'm%20taking%20more%20care%20to%20foster%20those%20kinds%20of%20connections%20and%20network%20because%20I%20will%20be%20here%20for%20longer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20did%20have%20non-negotiables%20that%20I%20would%20splurge%20on%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20absolutely%20necessary%20to%20dial%20it%20up%20on%20the%20things%20that%20are%20really%20important%20to%20you.%20Go%20all%20out%2C%20no%20holds%20barred.%20You%20know%20what%20you%20like%2C%20you%20know%20what%20you%20need%20%E2%80%94%20just%20do%20it%20and%20then%20cut%20mercifully%20everywhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prioritize%20travel%2C%20go%20take%20as%20many%20trips%20as%20you%20can.%20But%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20buy%20new%20clothes%20all%20the%20time%2C%20or%20you%20might%20not%20live%20where%20you%20want%20to%20because%20you%E2%80%99re%20traveling%20all%20the%20time.%20You%20are%20cutting%20back%20in%20other%20areas%20that%20don't%20matter%20to%20you%20and%20really%20just%20going%20all%20out%20in%20the%20areas%20that%20will%20give%20you%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Froi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EROI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20happiness%20and%20mental%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20manage%20to%20prioritize%20the%20things%20that%20were%20important%20to%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20year%20that%20I%20had%20enough%20vacation%20time%2C%20I%20went%20to%20see%20my%20sister%20in