m%2Fgadgets-news%2Fmotorola-launches-most-affordable-smartphone-running-android-14-moto-g04-price-specs-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F107719528.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Motorola%20launched%20the%20Moto%20g04%2C%20an%20entry-level%205G%20smartphone%2C%20with%20a%20PMMA%20acrylic%20glass%20finish.%20It%20has%20a%2090Hz%20IPS%20LCD%20punch-hole%20display%2C%20a%2016MP%20AI%20camera%20with%20a%20Quad%20Pixel%20camera%20system%2C%20and%20a%20massive%205000mAh%20battery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fmotorola-launches-most-affordable-smartphone-running-android-14-moto-g04-price-specs-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F107719528.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Bonds%20Worth%20Rs%2016%2C000%20Crore%20Sold%20Till%202022.%20Who%20Got%20How%20Much%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-scheme-violates-right-to-information-supreme-court-5061164%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20scrapping%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20the%20party%20received%20over%2060%25%20of%20the%20donations%20made%20under%20the%20scheme%20between%202016-2022.%20Just%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%202024%20polls%2C%20a%20five-judge%20bench%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20unconstitutional.%20The%20court%20said%20that%20the%20scheme%20infringes%20upon%20the%20citizens'%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-supreme-court-electoral-bonds-verdict-today-the-scheme-the-questions-and-the-defence-5060924%5C%22%3EElectoral%20bonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20financial%20instrument%20that%20allows%20individuals%20and%20businesses%20to%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20They%20were%20introduced%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%202018%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20cash%20donations.%20They%20were%20pitched%20as%20an%20initiative%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Election%20Commission%20data%2C%2028%2C030%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2016%2C437.63%20crore%20were%20sold%20between%202016%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20the%20primary%20beneficiary%20of%20these%20donations%20and%20received%20Rs%2010%2C122%20crore%2C%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations.%20The%20main%20opposition%20Congress%20party%20came%20a%20distant%20second%2C%20receiving%20Rs%201%2C547%20crore%20or%2010%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20while%20West%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20got%20Rs%20823%20crore%20or%208%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonations%20made%20to%20the%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20three%20times%20more%20than%20that%20of%20all%20other%2030%20parties%20combined%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20donations%20received%20by%20seven%20national%20parties%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%3A%20Rs%2010%2C122%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCongress%3A%20Rs%201%2C547%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnTMC%3A%20Rs%20823%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCPI(M)%3A%20Rs%20367%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnNCP%3A%20Rs%20231%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnBSP%3A%20Rs%2085%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCPI%3A%20Rs%2013%20crore%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEC%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20from%202017%20to%202022%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20over%20five%20times%20the%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20than%20the%20Congress%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20had%20been%20brought%20to%20curb%20black%20money%20and%20bring%20transparency%20into%20political%20donations%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinancial-support-to-political-parties-can-lead-to-quid-pro-quo-supreme-court-5061117%5C%22%3Eobjectives%20do%20not%20justify%20the%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20highlighted%20that%20alternative%20methods%20could%20effectively%20achieve%20these%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Flq9u46ag_bjp-generic-supporters-flag-pti_625x300_24_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20scrapping%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20as%20the%20party%20received%20over%2060%25%20of%20the%20donations%20made%20under%20the%20scheme%20between%202016-2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20Responds%20To%20Big%20Row%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20RSS%20Base%20In%20Sandeshkhali%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20political%20storm%20over%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20allowed%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20inciting%20trouble%20on%20the%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20allowed%20injustice%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20sent%20(representatives%20of)%20the%20state%20women's%20commission%20(to%20Sandeshkhali)%20immediately%20and%2017%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20shortly%20after%20main%20Opposition%20BJP%20staged%20a%20walkout%20over%20the%20raging%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlaming%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20unrest%20on%20the%20island%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20said%20the%20Centre%20had%20targeted%20local%20Trinamool%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20through%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20they%20entered%20the%20area%20and%20targeted%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20though%20ED%20and%20then%20they%20started%20the%20trouble%20there%20by%20getting%20people%20in.%20There%20is%20an%20RSS%20base%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20There%20were%20riots%20earlier%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%2C%20a%20local%20strongman%2C%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20for%20a%20month%20now%20after%20ED%20officials%20who%20visited%20the%20island%20to%20raid%20his%20home%20came%20under%20a%20mob%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20said%20a%20police%20team%20is%20meeting%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20%26quot%3BA%20police%20team%20of%20women%20are%20going%20door%20to%20door%20to%20see%20if%20there%20are%20any%20complaints.%20If%20they%20file%20a%20report%2C%20we%20will%20look%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeshkhali%20has%20hit%20headlines%20after%20a%20section%20of%20women%20there%20accused%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20The%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20allegations.%20The%20ruling%20party%20has%20trashed%20the%20charges%20and%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20unrest%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20island%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20an%20uneasy%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20visited%20Sandeshkhali%20yesterday%20and%20spoke%20to%20several%20women.%20The%20conversations%20revealed%20that%20while%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20of%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%20may%20not%20be%20true%2C%20many%20women%20were%20called%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20office%20at%20odd%20hours%20and%20threatened%20if%20they%20refused.%20Some%20women%20also%20said%20that%20their%20husbands%20were%20being%20tortured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20protests%20earlier%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20incidents%20must%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20otherwise%20why%20will%20the%20women%20say%20these%20things%3F%20You%20must%20enquire%20for%20yourself.%20Why%20else%20will%20women%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20speak%20out%3F%20Are%20they%20lying%3F%20There%20must%20be%20truth%20in%20these%20statements.%C2%A0We%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20We%20don't%20come%20out%20of%20our%20homes%20because%20of%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(Shahjahan's%20aides)%20would%20call%20women%20for%20meetings%20or%20rallies%20but%20there%20was%20no%20fixed%20time.%20It%20could%20be%20day%20or%20night.%20We%20would%20have%20to%20go%20whenever%20they%20called%20us%20and%20if%20we%20didn't%2C%20they%20would%20threaten%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20named%20Shahjahan's%20aides%2C%20Shibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%20While%20Sardar%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20Hazra%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20women%20alleged%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20leaders%20would%20torture%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20targeted%20women%20by%20picking%20up%20their%20husbands%20and%20beating%20them%20up%20with%20a%20stick%20in%20the%20party%20office.%20If%20we%20refused%20to%20go%20to%20the%20party%20office%2C%20they%20would%20pick%20up%20the%20men%20and%20thrash%20them%20so%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20have%20said%20a%20section%20of%20media%20is%20spreading%20%26quot%3Bwilful%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20to%20mislead%20people%20about%20the%20events%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20reiterated%20that%20no%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20torture%20of%20women%20have%20so%20far%20been%20received%20during%20the%20enquiries%20since%20conducted%20by%20the%20State%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20an%20all-women%2010-member%20fact-finding%20team%20led%20by%20DIG%20CID%2C%20and%20also%20the%20district%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F1q9e5as_sandeshkhali_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandeshkhali-row-5062193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20political%20storm%20over%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20allowed%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20inciting%20trouble%20on%20the%20island%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandeshkhali-row-5062193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandeshkhali-row-5062193%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-allowed-injustice-in-my-life-mamata-banerjee-on-sandeshkhali-row-5062193%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farooq%20Abdullah's%20Party%20To%20Fight%20Alone%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%20In%20Another%20Setback%20For%20INDIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20has%20declared%20its%20decision%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20dealing%20yet%20another%20setback%20to%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc.%20Party%20leader%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20categorically%20stated%20that%20the%20National%20Conference%20would%20contest%20the%20polls%20on%20its%20merit%20without%20entering%20into%20any%20alliance%20with%20other%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20seat%20sharing%20is%20concerned%2C%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20National%20Conference%20will%20contest%20elections%20on%20its%20own%20strength.%20There%20are%20no%20two%20opinions%20about%20it.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20questions%20on%20this%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-time%20former%20jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20was%20a%20strong%20votary%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20attended%20all%20the%20meetings%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%20Mr%20Abdullah%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20why%20his%20party%20took%20this%20sudden%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20no%20questions%20on%20this%20alliance%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Mr%20Abdullah%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20consensus%20on%20the%20India%20bloc's%20seat-sharing%20arrangements.%20Speaking%20on%20former%20Union%20minister%20Kapil%20Sibal's%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20stressed%20the%20urgency%20of%20reaching%20an%20agreement%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%20save%20the%20country%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20forget%20differences%20and%20think%20about%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20was%20recently%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20at%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association.%20The%20case%20involves%20the%20alleged%20siphoning%20off%20of%20funds%20through%20transfers%20to%20personal%20bank%20accounts%20of%20unrelated%20parties%20and%20unexplained%20cash%20withdrawals%20from%20the%20association's%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20skipped%20the%20summons%20and%20in%20an%20email%20and%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20ED%20officials%2C%20cited%20being%20out%20of%20town%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20his%20non-appearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fjce4kuc_farooq-abdullah-1200_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullahs-party-to-fight-alone-in-j-k-in-another-setback-for-india-5062239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Conference%20has%20declared%20its%20decision%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20dealing%20yet%20another%20setback%20to%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullahs-party-to-fight-alone-in-j-k-in-another-setback-for-india-5062239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullahs-party-to-fight-alone-in-j-k-in-another-setback-for-india-5062239%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullahs-party-to-fight-alone-in-j-k-in-another-setback-for-india-5062239%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Bridgerton%20season%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107719341%2Cimgsize-66868.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fbridgerton-season-3-teaser-penelope-and-colins-journey-from-friends-to-lovers%2Farticleshow%2F10771939