02-15-at-1.53.12-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20two%20days%20and%20two%20nights%20now%2C%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20trying%20to%20make%20their%20way%20to%20Delhi%20from%20Punjab%20have%20been%20attacked%20relentlessly%20with%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20rubber%20bullets%20at%20Shambhu%20Barrier%2C%20one%20of%20the%20borders%20that%20demarcates%20Punjab%20from%20Haryana.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20over%20100%20farmers%20have%20been%20injured.%20Journalists%20covering%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20spared%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20visuals%20emerging%20from%20Shambhu%20are%20difficult%20to%20watch%20%E2%80%93%20bloody%20heads%2C%20rubber%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebullet%20wounds%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20get%20tear%20gas%20out%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20eyes.%20For%20those%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20for%20any%20length%20of%20time%20or%20in%20any%20shape%20or%20form%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20in%202020-21%2C%20these%20scenes%20are%20even%20more%20difficult%20to%20watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%2C%20after%20all%2C%20the%20same%20farmers%20one%20visited%20several%20times%20at%20Tikri%20and%20Singhu%20and%20shared%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elangar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with.%20These%20are%20also%20the%20same%20people%20who%20showed%20incredible%20fortitude%20and%20courage%20as%20they%20braved%20heat%2C%20cold%2C%20rain%20and%20non-stop%20calumny%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20media.%20These%20are%2C%20indeed%2C%20the%20same%20simple%20and%20unassuming%20folk%20who%20showed%20the%20world%20yet%20again%20that%20Gandhian%20non-violent%20resistance%20is%20still%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20coming%20in%20from%20the%20Haryana-Punjab%20border%20is%20sporadic%2C%20as%20X%20and%20Facebook%20accounts%20of%20farmer%20leaders%20and%20journalists%20in%20the%20area%20have%20been%20shut%20down.%20One%20has%20to%20look%20through%20a%20lot%20of%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20watched%20videos%20of%20various%20journalists%20covering%20the%20situation%20at%20Shambhu%2C%20I%20spotted%20a%20farmer%20that%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLDyaogIbL1I%3Fsi%3DqJIlrBOqCTPNbYKU%5C%22%3Einterviewed%20at%20Tikri%20border%20in%20early%202021%20right%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20January%2026%20tractor%20rally%20that%20year.%20A%20giant%20of%20a%20man%2C%20he%20was%20difficult%20to%20forget.%20I%20remember%20his%20words%20had%20made%20an%20impression%20on%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLDyaogIbL1I%3Fsi%3DqJIlrBOqCTPNbYKU%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roads%20that%20the%20government%20has%20dug%20up%2C%20barricaded%2C%20hammered%20huge%20spikes%20into%20them%2C%20whose%20money%20were%20those%20roads%20built%20with%3F%20Our%20tax%20money.%20This%20is%20wrong.%20We%20are%20feeling%20very%20bad.%20They%20are%20calling%20us%20Khalistanis%20and%20terrorists.%20When%20we%20stand%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20borders%20and%20defend%20them%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20look%20like%20Khalistanis%20then%2C%20do%20we%3F%20First%20you%20use%20us%2C%20and%20then%20you%20call%20us%20Khalistanis.%20The%20tri-colour%20is%20precious%20to%20us%20because%20we%20have%20sacrificed%20so%20much%20to%20attain%20it!%20For%20them%20it%20may%20just%20be%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%2C%20but%20for%20us%2C%20the%20tri-colour%20is%20our%20life!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%5C%22%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20Protest%3A%20Modi%20Government%20Used%20British-Era%20Law%20to%20Give%20Itself%20Powers%20to%20Suspend%20Internet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20voice%20rose%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20talk%20about%20Modi%20and%20the%20state%20of%20democracy%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CDemocracy%20is%20in%20very%20bad%20shape%20in%20our%20country.%20They%20say%20India%20is%20the%20biggest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20is%20it%3F%20Modiji%2C%20you%20made%20so%20many%20promises%20before%20coming%20to%20power.%20You%20told%20us%20you%20are%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echowkidaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20we%20believed%20you%20and%20voted%20for%20you.%20But%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20fulfilled%20any%20of%20those%20promises.%20Has%20our%20income%20doubled%20as%20you%20promised%3F%20You%20said%20you%20would%20stand%20with%20the%20farmers%20through%20thick%20and%20thin%2C%20but%20every%20year%20you%20are%20decreasing%20our%20subsidy.%20Please%20read%20the%20Swaminathan%20commission%20report%20and%20give%20us%20our%20due!%20One%20last%20thing%2C%20did%20you%20see%20how%20they%20attacked%20us%20with%20tear%20gas%20as%20our%20convoy%20of%20tractors%20rolled%20into%20Delhi%20on%20November%2026%3F%20How%20can%20you%20treat%20people%20so%20inhumanely%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20that%20farmer%2C%20whose%20name%20unfortunately%20I%20did%20not%20record%2C%20literally%20nothing%20has%20changed.%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20has%20not%20become%20a%20legal%20guarantee%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20loans%20have%20not%20been%20forgiven%2C%20and%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20killings%20continue%20to%20go%20scot-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20practically%20impossible%20to%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20photos%20of%20the%20concrete%20barriers%20and%20concertina%20wire%20in%202020%20and%202024.%20All%20that%20has%20changed%20is%20that%20the%20government%20is%20now%20firing%20at%20the%20farmers%20with%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20using%20drones%20to%20attack%20them%20with%20tear%20gas%2C%20a%20cruel%20and%20sick%20joke%2C%20given%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20this%20poster%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd.png%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133504%2FGGNhRZsbcAAdMzd-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPoster%20about%20the%20Kisan%20Drone%20scheme.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20I%20have%20called%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20farmers%20I%20met%20during%20the%202020-21%20protests.%20The%20odds%20are%20stacked%20against%20them%2C%20but%20their%20voices%20reveal%20no%20trace%20of%20fear%20or%20anxiety.%20Perhaps%20that%20courage%20comes%20from%20the%20knowledge%20that%20they%20are%20fighting%20for%20justice.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20the%20outcome%20of%20this%20protest%20and%20attempted%20march%20to%20Delhi%20is%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20now%20stands%20completely%20exposed%20in%20its%20unwillingness%20and%20inability%20to%20keep%20any%20of%20its%20promises%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20farmers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2