electoral%20bonds%20and%20had%20challenged%20the%20scheme%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20on%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20scheme%2C%20CPI(M)%20Secretary-General%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BCPM%20was%20the%20only%20petitioner%2C%20the%20only%20political%20party%20who%20had%20the%20locus-standi%20to%20argue%20against%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%2C%20we%20are%20the%20only%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJFzI3fzhzV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJFzI3fzhzV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1758040415289135122%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20this.%20We%20are%20a%20petitioner%2C%20the%20only%20political%20party%20that%20had%20the%20locus%20standi%20to%20argue%20against%20electoral%20bonds.%20We%20are%20the%20only%20party%20that%20did%20not%20express%20any%20electoral%20bond%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%20because%20we%20consider%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20as%20a%20legalisation%20of%20political%20corruption%20and%20this%20had%20to%20be%20ended%2C%26quot%3B%20CPM%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20leader%20also%20said%20the%20court%20has%20significantly%20ordered%20that%20details%20of%20donations%20made%20through%20this%20method%20be%20made%20public.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20element%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20This%20has%20clearly%20exposed%20this%20government's%20claims%20of%20fighting%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yechury%20also%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20that%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%20contribution%26quot%3B%20by%20companies%20to%20political%20parties%20is%20antithetical%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20amendment%20was%20moved%20in%20Parliament%2C%20I%20was%20a%20member.%20I%20remember%20we%20had%20a%20very%20heated%20argument%20with%20the%20then%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20late%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20that%20you%20are%20opening%20up%20the%20way%20for%20money%20laundering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%2C%20calling%20the%20judgment%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBy%20this%20verdict%2C%20this%20unscrupulous%20scheme%20designed%20to%20finance%20the%20ruling%20party%20by%20anonymous%20corporate%20donors%20has%20been%20completely%20scrapped%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20out%20with%20an%20official%20response%20to%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20unanimous%20judgment%2C%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrchud%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20this%20morning%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20violates%20the%20citizens'%20right%20to%20information.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20directed%20that%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20must%20stop%20issue%20of%20these%20bonds%20at%20once%20and%20provide%20details%20of%20donations%20made%20through%20this%20mode%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20The%20poll%20body%20was%20asked%20to%20publish%20this%20information%20on%20its%20website%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707987300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2F3d23c5vg_sitaram-yechury-pti_625x300_24_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sitaram-yechury-cpm-electoral-bonds-supreme-courts-electoral-bond-verdict-gives-cpm