-107-60-cr-revenue-at-rs-4-166-71-cr-124021500760_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aditya%20Birla%20Fashion%20and%20Retail%20Ltd%20has%20reported%20a%20consolidated%20net%20loss%20of%20Rs%20107.60%20crore%20for%20the%20third%20quarter%20ended%20December%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fabfrl-q3-result-net-loss-at-rs-107-60-cr-revenue-at-rs-4-166-71-cr-124021500760_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fabfrl-q3-result-net-loss-at-rs-107-60-cr-revenue-at-rs-4-166-71-cr-124021500760_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fabfrl-q3-result-net-loss-at-rs-107-60-cr-revenue-at-rs-4-166-71-cr-124021500760_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Nigerian%20President's%20Sign%20Forged%20To%20Steal%20%246%20Million%20From%20Central%20Bank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENigeria%20is%20seeking%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Police%20Organisation's%20(Interpol's)%20help%20to%20arrest%20three%20suspects%20who%20allegedly%20stole%20%246.2%20million%20from%20the%20central%20bank%2C%20using%20the%20forged%20signature%20of%20of%20former%20President%20Muhammadu%20Buhari.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20funds%20were%20withdrawn%20in%20cash%20in%20January%20last%20year%2C%20a%20few%20months%20before%20Mr%20Buhari's%20term%20ended.%20Authorities%20believe%20that%20the%20suspects%20conspired%20with%20Nigeria's%20former%20central%20bank%20chief%20Godwin%20Emefiele%2C%20who%20is%20already%20on%20trial%20on%2020%20charges%2C%20including%20illegally%20receiving%20the%20%246.2%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Emefiele%20is%20the%20most%20high-profile%20former%20official%20to%20be%20charged%20with%20corruption%20since%20President%20Bola%20Tinubu%20took%20office%20in%20May.%20Although%20he%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20charges%20and%20is%20currently%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20authorities%20allege%20that%20Mr%20Emefiele%20unlawfully%20authorised%20the%20release%20of%20the%20money%20from%20the%20central%20bank%20vault%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20money%20was%20requested%20by%20the%20then%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20Federation%2C%20Boss%20Mustapha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Emefiele's%20alleged%20accomplices%20have%20been%20named%20as%20Adamu%20Abubakar%2C%20Imam%20Abubakar%20and%20Odoh%20Ocheme%2C%20a%20former%20central%20bank%20employee%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68282228%5C%22%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%2C%20citing%20the%20state-owned%20News%20Agency%20of%20Nigeria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20ordered%20their%20arrest%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20hours%20after%20Mr%20Mustapha%20testified%20in%20Mr%20Emefiele's%20trial.%20Mr%20Mustapha%20told%20the%20court%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Abuja%2C%20that%20neither%20he%20nor%20Mr%20Buhari%20had%20given%20their%20signature%20to%20approve%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20%246.2%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20signature%2C%20it%20is%20a%20faint%20attempt%20at%20reproducing%20%5Bformer%5D%20President%20Buhari's%20signature%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mustapha%20told%20the%20court.%20When%20shown%20the%20document%20used%20to%20withdraw%20the%20funds%2C%20Mr%20Mustapha%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20emanate%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20president%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdelta-flight-returns-to-amsterdam-after-maggots-fall-on-passengers-from-overhead-bin-5061175%5C%22%3EDelta%20Flight%20Returns%20To%20Amsterdam%20After%20Maggots%20Fall%20On%20Passengers%20From%20Overhead%20Bin%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20believe%20that%20Mr%20Emefiele%20falsified%20the%20documents%20in%20question%2C%20which%20requested%20the%20central%20bank%20to%20issue%20the%20money%20so%20that%20Mr%20Buhari%20could%20use%20them%20to%20pay%20foreign%20election%20observers.%20But%20in%20December%2C%20Mr%20Emefiele%20described%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bbarefaced%20lies%20told%20by%20the%20investigator%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20his%20satanic%20agenda%26quot%3B.%20He%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%20and%20transparent%20investigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutors%20believe%20that%20the%20three%20suspects%20have%20now%20left%20Nigeria.%20Therefore%2C%20authorities%20are%20seeking%20Interpol's%20help%20with%20their%20arrest%20and%20repatriation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Emefiele%20was%20appointed%20as%20central%20bank%20governor%20in%202014%20by%20then-President%20Goodluck%20Jonathan%2C%20with%20Mr%20Buhari%20reappointing%20him%20in%202019.%20He%20held%20the%20post%20until%20Mr%20Tinubu%20took%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-07%2Fmuhammadu-buhari_650x400_71436563706.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnigerian-ex-president-muhammadu-buharis-sign-forged-to-steal-6-million-from-central-bank-5061919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nigeria%20is%20seeking%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Police%20Organisation's%20(Interpol)%20help%20to%20arrest%20three%20suspects%20who%20allegedly%20stole%20%246.2%20million%20from%20the%20central%20bank%2C%20using%20the%20forged%20signature%20of%20of%20former%20President%20Muhammadu%20Buhari.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnigerian-ex-president-muhammadu-buharis-sign-forged-to-steal-6-million-from-central-bank-5061919%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnigerian-ex-president-muhammadu-buharis-sign-forged-to-steal-6-million-from-central-bank-5061919%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnigerian-ex-president-muhammadu-buharis-sign-forged-to-steal-6-million-from-central-bank-5061919%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers'%20Protest%3A%20Modi%20Government%20Used%20British-Era%20Law%20to%20Give%20Itself%20Powers%20to%20Suspend%20Internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133759%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-15-at-1.36.06-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20legislation%20invoked%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20give%20itself%20powers%20to%20block%20internet%20services%20in%20Punjab%20last%20week%20as%20farmers%20prepared%20to%20launch%20their%20protest%2C%20is%20a%20British-era%20law%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-used-british-era-act-to-block-internet-in-punjab-ahead-of-the-farmers-march%2Farticle67846087.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20context%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20emergency%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20safety%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20invoked%20its%20powers%20under%20the%20Temporary%20Suspension%20of%20Telecom%20Services%20(Public%20Emergency%20or%20Public%20Safety)%20Rules%2C%202017%20of%20the%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%2C%20to%20suspend%20internet%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2020%20police%20stations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20SAS%20Nagar%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Sri%20Mukhtsar%20Sahib%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20since%20last%20week%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20a%20Punjab%20government%20official%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20the%20power%20to%20issue%20such%20orders%20under%20the%20Rules%20and%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%20had%20not%20objected%20it.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana%20government%20issued%20orders%20to%20suspend%20internet%20services%20in%20that%20particular%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Fsuspension-of-telecom-services-internet-and-its-impact%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Esubmitted%20on%20December%202021%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20communications%20and%20information%20technology%20had%20observed%20that%20internet%20shutdowns%20have%20implications%20on%20national%20economy%2C%20freedom%20of%20press%2C%20education%20and%20healthcare%20services.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%20telecom%2Finternet%20shutdowns%20may%20be%20ordered%20on%20grounds%20of%20public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety.%20Public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety%20have%20not%20been%20defined%20in%20the%201885%20Act%20or%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Shashi%20Tharoor-led%20parliamentary%20committee%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20accounts%20on%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%20and%20Facebook%20which%20functioned%20as%20official%20pages%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20and%20unions%20ahead%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India%20seemingly%20upon%20government%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20like%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20Surjit%20Singh%20Phull%20from%20BKU%20Krantikari%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Harpal%20Sangha%2C%20Ashok%20Danoda%20from%20Haryana%20and%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%C2%A0%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20banned%20by%20the%20government.%20BKU%20(SBS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20farmer%20unions%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana.%20%E2%80%98Gaon%20Sawera%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20page%20run%20by%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20and%20his%20personal%20page%20has%20been%20withheld.%20Punia%20was%20arrested%20during%20the%202021%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984664000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133759%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-15-at-1.36.06-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20time%20the%20Union%20government%20suspended%20internet%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2020%20police%20stations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20SAS%20Nagar%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Sri%20Mukhtsar%20Sahib%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Companies'%20Donation%20To%20Political%20Parties%3A%20What%20Today's%20Verdict%20Changes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStriking%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20also%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%20political%20funding%26quot%3B%20by%20corporates%20and%20said%20it%20violated%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20The%20historic%20verdict%20effectively%20put%20the%20clock%20back%20on%20crucial%20amendments%20made%20to%20company%20laws%20when%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20brought%20this%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Was%20The%20Law%3F%20What%20Changed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Section%20182%20of%20Companies%20Act%2C%202013%20governs%20an%20Indian%20company's%20right%20to%20contribute%20to%20a%20political%20party.%20Prior%20to%20the%20amendments%2C%20this%20was%20governed%20by%20a%20set%20of%20conditions%20-%20the%20donation%20should%20be%20authorised%20by%20the%20Board%3B%20(ii)%20the%20donation%20cannot%20be%20made%20in%20cash%2C%20(iii)%20the%20donation%20must%20be%20disclosed%20in%20the%20Company's%20profit%20and%20loss%20account%20(iv)%20the%20company%20cannot%20donate%20more%20than%207.5%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20average%20profits%20for%20three%20years%20and%20(v)%20the%20company%20must%20disclose%20the%20name%20of%20the%20party%20it%20had%20donated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202017%20amendments%20removed%20the%20cap%20on%20the%20amount%20a%20company%20can%20donate%20and%20also%20with%20the%20requirement%20of%20disclosing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20party%20it%20had%20donated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Government%20Argued%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20arguments%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20had%20argued%20that%20anonymity%20ensures%20that%20the%20donor%20does%20not%20face%20retribution%20or%20victimisation.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20donor%20wants%20is%20that%20the%20other%20party%20should%20not%20know.%20Suppose%2C%20as%20a%20contractor%2C%20I%20donate%20to%20the%20Congress%20Party.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20know%20because%20it%20might%20form%20a%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20earlier%20cap%20on%20donations%20did%20not%20work%20because%20shell%20companies%20were%20created%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20political%20donations.%20The%20scheme%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20aimed%20at%20disincentivising%20the%20creation%20of%20such%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20view%20to%20discourage%20creation%20of%20shell%20companies%2C%20we%20did%20this...%20If%20companies%20want%20to%20donate%20more%20than%207.5%25%20of%20their%20net%20profit%2C%20let%20the%20discretion%20remain%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20said%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20cap%2C%20companies%20would%20switch%20to%20cash%20donations%2C%20bringing%20black%20money%20into%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Court%20Said%20Today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20down%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20amendment%20to%20the%20Companies%20Act%20now%20becomes%20otiose%20-%20meaning%20redundant.%20A%20company%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20has%20graver%20influence%20on%20the%20political%20process%20than%20contributions%20by%20individuals.%20%26quot%3BContributions%20by%20companies%20are%20purely%20business%20transactions.%20Amendment%20to%20Section%20182%20Companies%20Act%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20for%20treating%20companies%20and%20individuals%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said%20that%20before%20the%20amendments%2C%20loss-making%20companies%20were%20not%20able%20to%20contribute.%20But%20the%20amendment%20potentially%20enabled%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangement%20between%20a%20company%20running%20into%20losses%20and%20a%20political%20party.%20%26quot%3BThe%20amendment%20does%20not%20recognise%20the%20harm%20of%20allowing%20loss-making%20companies%20to%20contribute%20due%20to%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20The%20amendment%20to%20Section%20182%20Companies%20Act%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20for%20not%20making%20a%20distinction%20between%20loss%20making%20and%20profit%20making%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20holding%20the%20amendments%20to%20Companies%20Act%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20disclosure%20requirements%20in%20Section%20182(3)%20were%20included%20to%20ensure%20that%20corporate%20interests%20do%20not%20have%20an%20undue%20influence%20in%20electoral%20democracy%2C%20and%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20electorate%20must%20be%20made%20aware%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20states.%C2%A0%26quot%3BUnlimited%20contribution%20by%20companies%20to%20political%20parties%20is%20antithetical%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20because%20it%20allows%20certain%20persons%2Fcompanies%20to%20wield%20their%20clout%20and%20resources%20to%20influence%20policy%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F6k6p2298_money-generic_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-companies-and-electoral-bonds-how-supreme-court-verdict-undoes-big-change-5061700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Striking%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20also%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%20political%20funding%26quot%3B%20by%20corporates%20and%20said%20it%20violated%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-elector