22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt's%20His%20Right%26quot%3B%3A%20Jay%20Shah's%20No-Nonsense%20Take%20On%20Virat%20Missing%20ENG%20Tests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20backed%20India%20batting%20talisman%20Virat%20Kohli's%20decision%20to%20miss%20India's%20ongoing%20Test%20series%20against%20England%2C%20saying%20he%20has%20the%20right%20to%20ask%20for%20personal%20leave.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Rajkot%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20(SCA)%20stadium%20ahead%20of%20India's%20third%20Test%20against%20England%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20former%20India%20skipper%20is%20not%20someone%20who%20would%20ask%20for%20leave%20for%20no%20reason.%20He%20added%20that%20everyone%20should%20trust%20Kohli%20and%20back%20him.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20person%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%2015-year%20career%2C%20asks%20for%20personal%20leave%2C%20it's%20his%20right.%20Virat%20is%20not%20a%20player%20who%20will%20ask%20for%20leave%20for%20no%20reason.%20We%20need%20to%20trust%20our%20player%20and%20back%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20ESPNCricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%2C%2035%2C%20had%20initially%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20India%20team%20for%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20series%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons%20but%20later%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20entire%20five-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20last%20appearance%20came%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20earlier%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20will%20remain%20unavailable%20for%20selection%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20series%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%20The%20Board%20fully%20respects%20and%20supports%20Mr.%20Kohli's%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20when%20the%20BCCI%20secretary%20was%20asked%20whether%20Kohli%20would%20be%20part%20of%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June%2C%20Shah%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20talk%20about%20him%20%5Bsoon%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20confirmed%20that%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20would%20lead%20the%20'Men%20in%20Blues'%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20extraordinary%20T20%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20has%20the%20ability%2C%20we%20know.%20As%20he%20showed%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20where%20we%20won%2010%20matches%20in%20a%20row%20until%20the%20final.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20India%20will%20lift%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20under%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20captaincy%20in%20Barbados%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20last%20major%20trophy%20win%20was%20back%20in%202013%20when%20they%20beat%20England%20to%20win%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20the%20UK.%20Since%20then%2C%20India%20has%20shown%20incredible%20performances%20across%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cups%2C%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%2C%20but%20has%20fallen%20short%20every%20time%20of%20capturing%20the%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20will%20kick%20off%20on%20June%201%20and%20will%20be%20co-hosted%20by%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20the%20US.%20India%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20Group%20A%20alongside%20Ireland%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Canada%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Men%20in%20Blue%20will%20open%20their%20campaign%20against%20Ireland%20on%20June%205.%20Their%20second%20game%20of%20the%20tournament%20will%20be%20against%20arch-rival%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209.%20The%20final%20two%20games%20will%20be%20against%20Canada%20and%20USA%20on%20June%2012%20and%20June%2015%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20was%20on%20Wednesday%20renamed%20after%20ve