armers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20which%20organised%20the%202020%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20new%20leaflet%2C%20ahead%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%E2%80%99%20announced%20for%20February%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20including%20SKM%20Punjab%20led%20by%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%20and%20Darshan%20Pal%20and%20BKU%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20led%20by%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%20%E2%80%93%20also%20announced%20protests%20against%20the%20repression%20unleashed%20by%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20farmers%20trying%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20to%20fight%20for%20an%20MSP%20law%2C%20farm%20loan%20waiver%20and%20justice%20for%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20victims%20on%20February%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20call%20given%20by%20the%20SKM%20(nonpolitical)%20and%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20that%20they%20will%20be%20protesting%20the%20Haryana%20and%20Union%20governments%E2%80%99%20high-handedness%20against%20the%20protesting%20farmers.%20The%20SKM%20leadership%20held%20a%20meeting%20and%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Jalandhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20senior%20SKM%20leader%20Darshan%20Pal%20said%20that%20SKM%20Punjab%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20toll%20plazas%20free%20for%20the%20public%20to%20protest.%20%E2%80%9COver%20100%20farmers%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20protest%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Shambu%20border%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Reports%20have%20shown%20that%20rubber%20bullets%20used%20by%20the%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fdilli-chalo-62-more-farmers-injured-at-shambhu-khanauri-barriers-590775%5C%22%3Ehave%20injured%20close%20to%20130%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20Pal%20said%20that%20BKU%20Ekta%20Ugrahan%20and%20BKU%20Dakonda%20too%20have%20decided%20to%20lead%20a%20%E2%80%98Rail%20Roko%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%20Punjab%20from%2012%20noon%20to%204%20pm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20give%20a%20message%20to%20%5BHaryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%5D%20Khattar%20and%20the%20Centre%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20repression%20and%20injustice%20against%20farmers%20should%20be%20stopped.%20It%20is%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20right%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi.%20Those%20accused%20(paramilitary%20forces)%20who%20injured%20the%20farmers%20should%20be%20identified%20and%20cases%20should%20be%20filed%20against%20them.%20The%20situation%20is%20tense%20at%20the%20border%20and%20the%20government%20must%20play%20a%20role%20in%20diffusing%20the%20tension%2C%20else%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20farmers%E2%80%99%20anger%20will%20increase%20and%20the%20results%20of%20such%20a%20protest%20would%20not%20be%20good%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%2C%20BKU%20Ekta%20Ugrahan%20president%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%20said%20that%20they%20too%20have%20decided%20to%20protest%20the%20high-handedness%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Union%20governments%20in%20a%20four-hour%20%E2%80%98Rail%20Roko%E2%80%99%20on%20Thursday.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20condemn%20the%20way%20the%20Haryana%20police%20stopped%20the%20farmers%20and%20threw%20tear%20gas%20shells%20at%20them.%20We%20support%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20SKM%20nonpolitical%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%20and%20urge%20everybody%20to%20join%20the%20protest%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20BKU%20Rajewal%20president%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%20and%20other%20senior%20SKM%20leaders%20said%20that%20so%20far%2C%20they%20had%20not%20received%20any%20invitation%20from%20the%20SKM%20nonpolitical%20and%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%20farmer%20leaders%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20had%20not%20joined%20their%20protest.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20will%20be%20protesting%20against%20the%20atrocities%20of%20the%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20morcha%20farmers%2C%20who%20have%20been%20forcibly%20stopped%20from%20crossing%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%E2%80%99%20leaflet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20leaflet%2C%20which%20was%20being%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20SKM%20leadership%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20claiming%20that%20he%20is%20considering%20the%20poor%2C%20youth%2C%20women%20and%20farmers%20as%20the%20four%20%E2%80%98biggest%20castes%E2%80%99%20and%20his%20priority%20is%20to%20%E2%80%98respect%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98empower%E2%80%99%20them%2C%20but%20in%20practice%2C%20Modi%20is%20denigrating%20farmers%20and%20the%20other%20%E2%80%98three%20biggest%20castes%E2%80%99%20with%20an%20unprecedented%20vengeance%20for%20his%20corporate%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20vengeance%20on%20peasantry%20is%20because%20the%20monopoly%20capital%20in%20general%20and%20new%20monopoly%20house%20like%20Ambani%20and%20Adani%20in%20particular%20%E2%80%93%20which%20works%20closely%20with%20fascistic%20elements%20led%20by%20RSS-have%20identified%20peasant%20agriculture%20as%20a%20terrain%20for%20primitive%20capital%20accumulation.%20This%20was%20clear%20in%20a%20recent%20investigation%20by%20The%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%20which%20exposed%20how%20Adani%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20shaping%20notorious%20farm%20laws%20and%20larger%20corporation%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20leaders%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20leaflet%20that%20this%20investigation%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20detailed%20how%20the%20Adani%20group%20lobbied%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20April%202018%20by%20saying%20that%C2%A0%20the%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99Essential%20Commodities%20Act%E2%80%99%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20deterrence%20for%20industries%2Fentrepreneurs%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20first%20recorded%20instance%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20official%20advocacy%20for%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%20was%20carefully%20and%20loyally%20incorporated%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20in%20drafting%20draconian%20farm%20laws.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaflet%20states%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20investigation%20also%20exposed%20how%20Niti%20Ayog%20colluded%20with%20corporates%20to%20create%20a%20narrative%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98time%20is%20right%20to%20move%20from%20agriculture%20to%20agribusiness%E2%80%99%20and%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20anti-farmer%20farm%20laws%20and%20corporatization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A6The%20much-hyped%20project%20for%20digitising%20agriculture%20too%20has%20a%20hidden%20agenda%20for%20furthering%20corporate%20penetration.%20This%20became%20very%20evident%20when%20the%20Modi%20regime%20forced%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR)%20to%20sign%20multiple%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoUs)%20with%20Bayer%2C%20a%20leading%20multinational%20agri%20big%20business%20house%20and%20Amazon%20Kisan%2C%20the%20e-commerce%20giant%20for%20research%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20name%20of%20empowering%20small%20holder%20farmers%2C%20these%20MoUs%20are%20designed%20to%20deepen%20corporate%20tentacles%20over%20peasantry.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20shrewd%20attempt%20to%20bring%20pro%20corporate%20draconian%20farm%20laws-maximize%20corporate%20profits-through%20the%20backdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20aggressively%20promoting%20%E2%80%9CAtma%20Nirbhar%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20hallmark%20of%20his%20hyper%20nationalism%2C%20is%20drastically%20cutting%20funds%20to%20public%20agricultural%20research%2C%2