ctive%20listing%20or%20non-listing%20of%20cases%2C%20the%20shift%20from%20an%20open-court%20system%20to%20a%20closed-door%20email-based%20system%2C%20and%20non-compliance%20with%20rules%20and%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20in%20allocating%20cases%20to%20benches%2C%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmaster%20of%20roster%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F864783%2Fdemocracy-will-not-survive-if-problems-not-fixed-four-top-supreme-court-judges%5C%22%3Ewas%20criticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20of%20the%20four%20senior%20most%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20January%202018.%20In%20that%20unprecedented%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20judges%20had%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20potential%20misuse%20of%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20on%20and%20several%20Chief%20Justices%20later%2C%20the%20perceived%20concerns%20remain%20and%20there%20has%20been%20little%20movement%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20court%20as%20an%20institution%20to%20address%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstances%20of%20cases%20not%20being%20listed%20despite%20judicial%20orders%20have%20been%20noted%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20registry%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20and%20its%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20issues%20expected%20to%20be%20discussed%20include%20the%20alleged%20allocation%20of%20politically%20sensitive%20cases%20to%20specific%20benches%2C%20sometimes%20in%20violation%20of%20established%20rules%20and%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20civil%20liberties%20and%20political%20rights%20has%20become%20critical%20amidst%20a%20surge%20in%20arrests%20of%20activists%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20politicians%20by%20central%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Authority%20on%20questionable%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDraconian%20provisions%20in%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20and%20Narcotics%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%20grant%20these%20agencies%20increased%20powers%2C%20enabling%20prolonged%20detention%2C%20use%20of%20confessions%20in%20trials%2C%20and%20limited%20access%20to%20bail%20for%20the%20accused.%20This%20necessitates%20a%20vigilant%20judiciary%20to%20prevent%20the%20abuse%20of%20power%20by%20central%20agencies%20targeting%20opposition%20parties%20or%20government%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20discuss%20these%20issues%2C%20three%20sessions%20will%20be%20conducted%20on%20February%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20session%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Supreme%20Court%20Judicial%20Administration%20%26amp%3B%20Management%20%E2%80%93%20Issues%20and%20Concerns%E2%80%99%2C%20will%20be%20held%20from%2010%20am%20to%201%20pm.%20It%20will%20be%20moderated%20by%20Alok%20Prasanna%2C%20co-founder%20Vidhi%20Centre%20for%20Legal%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speakers%20include%20Justices%20Madan%20Lokur%20and%20Kurien%20Joseph%2C%20former%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3B%20Justice%20Ajit%20Prakash%20Shah%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20Delhi%20high%20court%3B%C2%A0Justice%20Rekha%20Sharma%2C%20former%20judge%2C%20Delhi%20high%20court%3B%C2%A0Justice%20Govind%20Mathur%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20Allahabad%20high%20court%3B%20Kamini%20Jaiswal%2C%20advocate%2C%20Supreme%20Court%3B%20and%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20Advocate%20and%20convenor%2C%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20%26amp%3B%20Reforms%20(CJAR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20session%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20recent%20trend%20on%20cases%20involving%20Civil%20Liberties%20and%20Political%20Rights%20%E2%80%98%20will%20be%20held%20from%202%20pm%20to%205%20pm.%20It%E2%80%99ll%20be%20moderated%20by%20Anjali%20Bharadwaj%2C%20Right%20to%20Information%20activist%2C%20Satark%20Nagrik%20Sanghatan%20and%20CJAR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speakers%20include%3A%20Justices%20A.K.%20Patnaik%20and%20Indira%20Banerjee%2C%20former%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3B%20professor%20Mohan%20Gopal%2C%20former%20director%2C%20National%20Judicial%20Academy%3B%20senior%20advocates%20Trideep%20Pais%2C%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20Mihir%20Desai%3B%20and%20Warisha%20Farasat%2C%20advocate%2C%20Delhi%20high%20court%20and%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20session%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20resolutions%20and%20the%20way%20forward.%20It%E2%80%99ll%20be%20moderated%20by%20Indira%20Unninayar%2C%20advocate%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Amrita%20Johri%2C%20RTI%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707964219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fseminar-on-scs-judicial-trends-and-civil-liberties-to-be-held-in-new-delhi-on-february-24%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%20issues%20expected%20to%20be%20covered%20are%20selective%20listing%20or%20non-listing%20of%20cases%2C%20the%20shift%20from%20an%20open-court%20system%20to%20a%20closed-door%20email-based%20system%2C%20and%20non-compliance%20with%20rules%20and%20procedures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fseminar-on-scs-judicial-trends-and-civil-liberties-to-be-held-in-new-delhi-on-february-24%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pfizer%20agrees%20to%20pay%20%2493%20million%20to%20settle%20Lipitor%20drug%20antitrust%20lawsuit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707964171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-05%2F21%2Ffull%2F1621601765-406.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpfizer-agrees-to-pay-93-million-to-