3EThunderstorms%20caused%20flooding%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20capital%2C%20Jakarta%2C%20with%20Reuters%20news%20agency%20reporting%20that%20dozens%20of%20polling%20stations%20had%20been%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20main%20contenders%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20for%20the%20presidency%20has%20seen%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwho-are-indonesias-presidential-hopefuls%2Fa-67267495%5C%22%3Ethree%20main%20candidates%20emerge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20opinion%20polls%20ahead%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20the%20man%20leading%20the%20race%20is%20Prabowo%20Subianto%20from%20the%20Gerindra%20Party%2C%20a%20former%20military%20commander%20who%20currently%20serves%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%20is%20up%20against%20Ganjar%20Pranowo%20from%20the%20Indonesian%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Struggle%20and%20Anies%20Baswedan%2C%20the%20former%20governor%20of%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third-largest%20democracy%20with%20around%20205%20million%20voters%20eligible%20to%20cast%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbiggest-election-year-2024%5C%22%3EIndia%2C%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%A6Is%202024%20the%20Biggest%20Election%20Year%20Ever%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20at%20stake%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Southeast%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20economy%2C%C2%A0Indonesia%C2%A0has%20experienced%20stability%20and%20growth%20under%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%20All%20three%20presidential%20contenders%20have%20made%20similar%20promises%20to%20continue%20in%20that%20vein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProbowo%20is%20the%20only%20candidate%20with%20ties%20to%20the%C2%A0era%20of%20Suharto%20dicatorship%2C%20a%20time%20marked%20by%20brutality%20and%20corruption.%20He%20was%20a%20special%20