content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20find%20your%20soulmate%20after%20you%20reach%20the%20age%20of%2050%3F%20Apparently%2C%20at%20Madhav%20Damle%E2%80%99s%20Happy%20Seniors%2C%20a%20one-time%20membership%20fee%20of%20Rs%207%2C000.%20A%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20happiness%20of%20the%20150-odd%20people%20who%20have%20found%20companionship%20through%20the%20matchmaking%20agency%20is%20proof%20of%20its%20success%20rate.%20Whenever%20the%20topic%20of%20love%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20silver%20years%20is%20addressed%2C%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20think%20back%20to%20the%20year%202015.%20If%20you%20recall%2C%20there%20was%20a%20story%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338685%2Fsenior-citizen-woman-paragliding-paramotoring-viral-video-on-x-twitter-adventure-sports-usha-thuse-anand-mahindra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20couple%20in%20their%20sixties%3C%2Fa%3E%20finding%20love.%20It%20broke%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannels%20and%20digital%20publications%20cited%20the%20story%20as%20proof%20of%20the%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20relationships%20were%20perceived%20in%20India%20and%20the%20acceptance%20of%20more%20modern%20ideologies.%20But%2C%20while%20we%20may%20like%20to%20think%20that%20live-in%20relationships%20have%20gotten%20their%20blessing%20from%20society%2C%20it%20is%20still%20taboo%20in%20many%20places%20and%20an%20unspoken%20sacrilege%20in%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20Anil%20Yardi%20and%20Asawari%20Kulkarni%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdating%20in%20old%20age%E2%80%9D%20story%20emerged%2C%20the%20world%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20conversation%20starter%20to%20how%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336383%2Fhomemade-hyderabadi-biryani-in-bengaluru-by-noons-biryani-couple-entrepreneurs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%2