nvestigate-davos-ski-shop-over-no-equipment-for-jews-sign-13071283%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mother%20appears%20in%20court%20charged%20with%20murder%20of%20six-year-old%20son%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707894540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-matthew-healy-ireland_6455199.jpg%3F20240214110027%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fruth-purcell-healy-mother-appears-in-court-charged-with-murder-of-six-year-old-son-13071269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20has%20appeared%20in%20court%20in%20Ireland%20charged%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20her%20six-year-old%20son.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fruth-purcell-healy-mother-appears-in-court-charged-with-murder-of-six-year-old-son-13071269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fruth-purcell-healy-mother-appears-in-court-charged-with-murder-of-six-year-old-son-13071269%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fruth-purcell-healy-mother-appears-in-court-charged-with-murder-of-six-year-old-son-13071269%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%203000%20Babies%20With%20Congenital%20Heart%20Diseases%20Have%20Been%20Saved%20By%20This%20Inspiring%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20Khatoon%20(26)%20remembers%2022%20February%2C%202023%2C%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday%2C%20as%20she%20welcomed%20her%20first%20child%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-infant-pregnancy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20into%20the%20world.%20She%20was%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital%20after%20eight%20days%20and%20was%20all%20set%20for%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20that%20a%20new%20mother%20has%20to%20face.%20But%20two%20days%20after%20she%20went%20home%20with%20her%20bundle%20of%20joy%2C%20the%20concerned%20Kolkata%20resident%20started%20noticing%20alarming%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010-day-old%20baby%20was%20turning%20blue%20when%20he%20cried.%20They%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20a%20doctor%2C%20who%20diagnosed%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%2C%20and%20advised%20the%20parents%20to%20take%20the%20baby%20to%20a%20bigger%20hospital.%20Wahida%20recounts%20that%20her%20son%20was%20then%20diagnosed%20with%20Congenital%20Heart%20Disease%20(CHD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECHDs%20are%20present%20at%20birth%20and%20can%20affect%20the%20structure%20of%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%20and%20the%20way%20it%20works.%20They%20can%20affect%20how%20blood%20flows%20through%20the%20heart%20and%20out%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20body.%20CHDs%20can%20vary%20from%20mild%20(such%20as%20a%20small%20hole%20in%20the%20heart)%20to%20severe%20(such%20as%20missing%20or%20poorly%20formed%20parts%20of%20the%20heart).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F30745481%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%20that%20nine%20out%20of%201%2C000%20babies%20have%20CHD.%20In%20India%2C%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20babies%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20this%20condition%20annually.%20One-fifth%20of%20these%20babies%20will%20likely%20need%20intervention%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20their%20life%2C%20due%20to%20a%20serious%20birth%20defect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%2C%20though%2C%20is%20twofold%2C%20as%20early%20and%20timely%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20this%20disease.%20But%20specialised%20care%20is%20lacking%20in%20most%20government%20institutions%2C%20which%20causes%20a%20financial%20constraint%20on%20parents%20with%20low%20incomes%2C%20like%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20found%20help%20through%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20timely%20intervention%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341760%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202009%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20works%20for%20the%20health%20and%20well-being%20of%20marginalised%20and%20rural%20communities.%20As%20the%20foundation%20worked%20closely%20with%20children%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20it%20soon%20realised%20the%20need%20for%20better%20medical%20facilities%20and%20early%20intervention%20for%20the%20underprivileged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interactions%20with%20doctors%2C%20they%20found%20that%20a%20major%20area%20which%20needed%20attention%20was%20CHD%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20birth%20defects%20in%20newborns.%20The%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%202017%20found%20that%20CHD%20was%20the%20seventh%20biggest%20contributor%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261889%2Fjharkhand-reduce-infant-maternal-mortality-rate-doctor-couple-quits-job%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20infant%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20caused%201.8%20lakh%20infant%20deaths%20in%202017.%20As%20such%2C%20in%202013%2C%20the%20foundation%20started%20working%20to%20provide%20aid%20for%20surgical%20interventions%20for%20children%20born%20with%20congenital%20heart%20defects%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20leading%20hospitals%20in%20the%20country%2C%20under%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%20Program%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongenital%20Heart%20Disease%20(CHD)%20holds%20the%20foremost%20position%20globally%20in%20causing%20deaths%20linked%20to%20birth%20defects%2C%20persisting%20as%20a%20significant%20contributor%20to%20mortality%20and%20morbidity%20in%20both%20paediatric%20populations%20of%20developing%20and%20developed%20nations.%20In%20India%20only%2C%20it%20accounts%20for%2010%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%2C%20despite%20notable%20advancements%20in%20diagnosing%20and%20treating%20CHDs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Viresh%20Mahajan%2C%20Director%20of%20Paediatric%20Cardiac%20Sciences%20%26amp%3B%20Scientific%20Director%20of%20Clinical%20Research%2C%20Sarvodaya%20Hospital%2C%20Faridabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetecting%20congenital%20heart%20disease%20is%20possible%20during%20prenatal%20and%20postnatal%20stages%20through%20diverse%20diagnostic%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20sensitivity%20is%20critical%2C%20as%20any%20delay%20can%20prove%20fatal%20for%20infants.%20Timely%20treatment%20is%20very%20important%20as%20a%20child%20can%20lead%20a%20normal%20life%20in%20most%20congenital%20heart%20defects%20if%20treated%20at%20the%20optimal%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20state%20that%20early%20intervention%20is%20key.%20Dr%20Mahajan%20adds%20that%20children%20with%20CHD%20can%20lead%20healthy%20and%20lengthy%20lives%20with%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Early%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20CHD%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%