f%20the%20parents%2C%20but%20faced%20with%20a%20massive%20bill%20of%20over%20Rs%203%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20treated%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%2C%20Wahida%20was%20asked%20to%20visit%20a%20specialist%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%2C%20R%20N%20Tagore%20Hospital%2C%20Kolkata.%20Here%2C%20the%20doctor%20assessed%20the%20baby%20and%20diagnosed%20him%20with%20a%20Ventricular%20Septal%20Defect%20(VSD)%2C%20which%20needed%20surgery.%20The%20surgery%20(done%20when%20the%20baby%20was%201.5%20months%20old)%20would%20cost%20over%20Rs%203.5%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Aslan%2C%20works%20as%20a%20salesman%20with%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20per%20annum.%20As%20they%20explained%20their%20situation%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20they%20got%20help%20through%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20which%20financially%20supported%20the%20surgery.%20The%20baby%20also%20needed%20an%20open%20heart%20surgery%20in%20January%202024%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20Rs%204.8%20lakh.%20This%20too%2C%20was%20supported%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20timely%20intervention%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298516%2Fengineer-quits-job-to-make-natural-baby-food-mixes-earns-lakhs-tummy-friendly-sridevi-ashala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20is%20now%20well%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20meeting%20all%20his%20milestones%20just%20like%20any%20other%20infant%2C%20says%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%203%2C000%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%2015%20hospitals%20across%20the%20country.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341761%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%2015%20hospitals%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20working%20on%20solving%20the%20financial%20problems%20as%20these%20surgeries%20are%20very%20expensive%20for%20the%20common%20man.%20But%20this%20one%20surgery%20can%20save%20a%20child%20and%20improve%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20CHD%20requires%20immediate%20paediatric%20cardiac%20care%2C%20either%20in%20the%20first%20month%20or%20first%20year%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20certain%20instances%2C%20surgery%20may%20be%20imperative%20within%20the%20initial%20hours%20or%20days%20of%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Hence%2C%20early%20diagnosis%20and%20timely%20management%20stand%20as%20pivotal%20elements%20in%20the%20treatment%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%2015%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Heart%20Institute%2C%20Wockhardt%20Hospital%2C%20Fortis%2C%20Apollo%2C%20The%20Narayana%20Group%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20country.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20get%20surgery%20as%20soon%20as%20required%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%2026-day-old%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20provides%20this%20financial%20support%20to%20patients%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20below%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20and%20children%20below%20the%20age%20of%2020.%20The%20Little%20Hearts%20Programme%20supports%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20surgeries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20procedures%20such%20as%20Atrial%20Septal%20Defect%20(ASD)%2C%20Ventricular%20Septal%20Defect%20(VSD)%2C%20Tetralogy%20of%20Fallot%20(ToF)%20and%20more%20complex%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20providing%20immediate%20financial%20assistance%2C%20the%20foundation%20also%20offers%20post-surgery%20care%2C%20which%20is%20equally%20vital.%20In%20cases%20where%20parents%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20medications%20or%20specialist%20fees%2C%20the%20foundation%20extends%20support.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20conduct%20awareness%20programmes%20in%20collaboration%20with%20hospitals%20to%20ensure%20that%20parents%20are%20knowledgeable%20about%20symptoms%20and%20know%20when%20to%20seek%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20should%20remain%20vigilant%20and%20not%20overlook%20common%20congenital%20heart%20disease%20(CHD)%20symptoms%20in%20newborns%2C%20including%20challenges%20in%20feeding%2C%20rapid%20breathing%2C%20or%20bluish%20skin%20discolouration%2C%20as%20early%20recognition%20is%20crucial%20for%20timely%20intervention%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20response%20to%20the%20programme%20and%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20help%20more%20children%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20now%20expanding%20its%20intervention%20under%20The%20Hans%20Paediatric%20Care%20programme%20that%20will%20focus%20on%20various%20aspects%20of%20child%20health.%20It%20hopes%20to%20partner%20with%20more%20hospitals%20to%20provide%20financial%20access%20to%20families%20and%20build%20a%20world%20where%20every%20child%20has%20equal%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20parents%20like%20Wahida%2C%20this%20financial%20assistance%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20through%20such%20a%20tough%20time%20when%20I%20suddenly%20discovered%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261081%2Findia-buy-online-ergonomic-baby-carrier-cost-features-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10-day-old%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20heart%20problem.%20While%20I%20got%20the%20diagnosis%20soon%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20arrange%20the%20money.%20My%20baby%20is%20hale%20and%20healthy%20today%2C%20all%20thanks%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20surgery%2C%20babies%20can%20lead%20a%20normal%20life.%20What%20advice%20does%20Dr%20Changela%20give%20his%20patients%3F%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20thing%20I%20tell%20parents%20who%20ask%20me%20about%20what%20precautions%20they%20should%20take%20is%20to%20be%20free%20of%20worry!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707886457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congenital%20heart%20diseases%20affect%20over%202%20lakh%20babies%20in%20India%20per%20year.%20Over%203000%20such%20babies%20were%20saved%20by%20the%20timely%20intervention%20and%20financial%20help%20provided%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided