ease%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scaled-up%20process%20successfully%20produced%20100%20to%20150%20kg%20of%20vermicompost%20within%20a%20month%20from%20250%20to%20300%20kg%20of%20daily%20waste%20fed.%20The%20increased%20earthworm%20count%20resulted%20in%20the%20secondary%20end%20product%20being%20the%20earthworm%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20study%20included%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetable%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20aquatic%20weed%20(water%20hyacinth)%20as%20prime%20substrates%2C%20both%20in%20mono-substrate%20composting%20and%20co-composting.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20entire%20study%2C%20we%20have%20converted%2015%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20collected%20from%20the%20markets%20and%20ponds%20around%20the%20IIT%20Guwahati%20campus%20(350%20kg%20per%20day).%20The%20confidence%20that%20we%20gained%20through%20the%20study%20is%20the%20basis%20on%20which%20we%20are%20suggesting%20that%20the%20technology%20can%20handle%20sizable%20quantities.%20We%20believe%20this%20process%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20reshape%20organic%20waste%20treatment%20facilities%20globally%2C%20providing%20an%20environmentally%20compatible%20solution%20to%20mitigate%20contamination%20hazards%20and%20produce%20an%20outstanding%20soil%20conditioner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20IIT-Guwahati)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707746351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-Guwahati-Vermicompost-Earthworms-1707743947.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341515%22%2C%22summ